```

Here `m_Value(Dividend)` captures the dividend from the udiv, and then `m_Specific(Dividend)` is used to match the same value in the urem. But since `m_Specific` binds at pattern construction time, not match time, this won't work!

The fix should be to use `m_Deferred(Dividend)` and `m_Deferred(Divisor)` instead of `m_Specific(Dividend)` and `m_Specific(Divisor)`.

